ext_descriptions.ext_description:
the string that specifies the type of the characteristic that is represented.

Where applicable, the following values shall be used:


'centre of mass': the characteristic is the centre of the mass of the characterized_item, evaluated or required independently of any representation of the characterized_item;

'centroid': the characteristic is the centre of mass of a body as
evaluated from a geometric representation of the characterized_item;

An instance of Representation_relationship may be used to relate the shape_characteristic with the Geometric_model from which the centroid was computed.




'moment of inertia': the characteristic is the 3*3 matrix of inertia of the characterized_item;

'surface area': the characteristic is the extent of the surface of the characterized_item;

'volume': the characteristic is the volume of the characterized_item;
